
-Service Domain in Kubernetes
  - A Service Doimain (SD) maps into a kubernetes namespace (OpenShift project). 
    It a composition of (banking) functional code which run on any type of runtime and non functional capabilities (technical), eg. a rule engine or a event broker for event propagation.
    
    
-  Standards and API for business modules
A business component contract is described and made operational via API, which are managed by an API management system
 - Modeling
 - Versioning 
 - APIs to Service Domain mapping and rounting
 
 - Choreograpy amond Service Domains
    - Event Driven Architecture approah to choreography
    - API,  Message passing, Streaming, Shared Data
    
    

